  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3608495/" class="title-link">鱼死网不破——评《苍黄》</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3608495"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/baibo/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1093185-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/baibo/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">不夜影城</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-08-29"
      class="main-meta">2010-08-29 15:06:38</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3608495_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  读罢《苍黄》，感触有三：怕、很怕、非常怕。其实这也正应了书名，苍黄，通仓皇，意为匆促而慌张。书中那些混迹官场之人，别管那场是大是小，尚且如此，何况无权无势的老百姓，所以我很怕。更让我害怕的是，那些原本在官场这个局中混的人五人六、风风光光之人，无论猖狂与谨慎...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3608495/#comments">(10回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">14有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
